
                   HARD DRIVE INSTALL

Copy all files into a drawer

Datastore1.1
All Figs
The icon Datastore1.1Docs.info 
     and Datastore1.1Doc file 


 All files are crunched with power packer you will need to run 
power packer patch (which is c:pp) or decrunch all the text files 
first.

 You will need to assign DS: to your drawer
 
                  
 Script for Datastore1.1 Docs with all files copied to 
 dh0:serious/DBases/Datastore/docs/"


                   
assign DS: "dh0:serious/DBases/Datastore/docs/"
sys:c/pp                ; only need if files not uncrunched
sys:c/wait 2
sys:c/amigaguide datastore1.1
sys:c/waitreturn        ; waits till program has finished then asks you to 
                          press return, the rest of the script carrys on 
sys:c/pp                ; will remove power packer patch
assign DS: dismount     ; will remove assigns



                  
